Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.41,0:00:18.65,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.65,0:00:24.35,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,My apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.35,0:00:28.26,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,I will cover the cleaning bill, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.26,0:00:32.59,Serifa Std,,0,0,2,,{\fs23}I know it's not much of an apology,\Nbut if you'd like, may I give you a ride?
